XOR-RAID
========
A metamodule for the md driver of the Linux kernel which supports
variable de-/encoding using XOR equations.

Ein Metamodul für den md-Treiber des Linux-Kernels das variable
De-/Kodierung über XOR-Gleichungen unterstützt.

Not included is the tool for generating the equations/configuration
files.  Some examples are in the data folder, but'll need the used tool
(cauchyrs), or some other to generate them for other situations.

The performance isn't extraordinary, but it works.  See BUGS for
exceptions to that rule.

